Popular Nigerian Instagram comedian, Broda Shaggi celebrates his birthday today, 18 September 2019. Broda Shaggi is known for his funny skits and the “oya hit me” signature pose which have made him a lot of followers on social media. The comedian could also be called an artist after his release of “Ori”, “Nor Nor” and numerous songs after making his way into Davido’s 30 billion gang crew. HAPPY BIRTHDAY BRODA SHAGGI!! Source